Since `φ` is `V ≃ₗ[ℚ] V`, `φ` restricts to `L ≃ₗ[ℚ] L`. Therefore, `fun x ↦ c_v (φ x)` is an automorphism of `L ⊗[ℤ] v.adicCompletion ℚ` because `c_v` is an isomorphism and `φ` restricts to an isomorphism on `L`.

